          t
          
            m
          
        
        ]
        .
      
    
    {\displaystyle R[t_{1},t_{2},\cdots ]=\varinjlim R[t_{1},t_{2},\cdots ,t_{m}].}
  
The algebraic closure of finite fields of the same characteristic 
  
    
      
        
          
            
              
                F
              
              ¯
            
          
          
