   and is denoted by 
  
    
      
        k
        (
        
          
            p
          
        
        )
        .
      
    
    {\displaystyle k({\mathfrak {p}}).}
  
If M is a left R-module, then the localization of M with respect to S is given by a change of rings 
  
    
      
