   denotes the exponent of p in the prime factorization of a nonzero integer n into prime numbers (we also put 
  
    
      
        
          |
        
        0
        
          
            |
          
          
            p
          
        
        =
        0
      
    
    {\displaystyle |0|_{p}=0}
   and 
  
    
      
        
