          |
        
        n
        
          
            |
          
          
            p
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle |m/n|_{p}=|m|_{p}/|n|_{p}}
  ). It defines a distance function on 
  
    
      
        
          Q
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle \mathbb {Q} }
   and the completion of 
  
    
      
        
          Q
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle \mathbb {Q} }
   as a metric space is denoted by 
  
    
      
        
          
            Q
          
          
            p
          
        
